!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Sau khi v sinh sch s cn hng kh da t nhin trc khi ct gi  trnh da b nm mc</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"huong_dan_cach_ve_sinh_tui_da_trang_hieu_qua_tuc_thi\">Hng dn cch v sinh ti da trng hiu qu tc th</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"lam_sach_tui_da_trang_bang_nuoc_am\">Lm sch ti da trng bng nc m</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>y l cch lm sch ti da trng hiu qu v v cng n gin, c rt nhiu ngi la chn. Cc tin hnh rt d dng:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000230642/file/ve-sinh-tui-da_51f18196de6d4a038770eec92f2ab97d.png\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Bn dng mt cht nc m  lm sch ti da</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 1:</strong>&nbsp;Pha nc m  nhit  va phi vi mt t x phng vi nng  nh, khuy   hn hp c ha tan vi nhau</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 2:</strong>&nbsp;Dng mt chic khn mm, thm hn hp sau  lau nh nhng v nhiu ln  nhng vng b dnh bn  vt bn c lm sch</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 3:</strong>&nbsp;Bn tin hnh lau khp b mt ti da  v sinh tng th cho sn phm  chic ti tr nn bng long v trng nh mi</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Lu  nh: i vi chiu ti xch da hay cc mn  da khc bn khng nn git trc tip chng vi x phng v s lm lp da nhanh hng. Ngoi ra, khng nn s dng nc qu nng v phi  ni c nh sng mnh, iu ny s lm lp da trn ti b bong trc, nhanh hng hn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"dung_kem_danh_rang\">Dng kem nh rng</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kem nh rng cng c xem l cht dng  ty ra cc vt bn, c bit l vt bn trn ti da. Va n gin va khng tn chi ph vi cc bc nh sau:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000230642/file/ve-sinh-tui-da-3_584722fa0e424bc2b7af0dccb9d79de5.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Kem nh rng s gip lm sng bng ti da trng</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 1:</strong>&nbsp;Bi mt t kem nh rng ln b mt bn chi c, sau  ch nh nhng ln b mt ti  b bn cho n khi sch th dng li</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 2:</strong>&nbsp;S dng khn m lau qua khu va lm sch bng kem nh rng,  mt lc cho ti kh l bn  c mt chic ti da trng mi nh ban u</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"lam_sach_tui_da_trang_bi_bang_con\">Lm sch ti da trng b bng cn</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cn cng l mt trong nhng loi nguyn liu thng xuyn p dng  lm sch b mt ti da. c bit cht ny cn c th ty c sch cc ti da b dnh mu. Cch thc hin n gin vi 3 bc:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000230642/file/ve-sinh-tui-da-4_6494c508e63e48859c0dd53399c482cd.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Cn c tc dng ty sch ti da b dnh bn cng u</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 1:</strong>&nbsp;S dng bng ty trang hoc tm bng nhng vo cn sau  thoa ln vt bn trn b mt ti</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 2:&nbsp;</strong>Dng khn trng sch thm nc m lau sch li b mt ti xch da</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 3:</strong>&nbsp; ti xch  ni thong mt  kh hon ton s c c din mo p mi nh lc ban u</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"ve_sinh_tui_da_bang_chanh_va_muoi\">V sinh ti da bng chanh v mui</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> c th ty sch nhng vt bn cng u trn ti da, bn c th kt hp 2 loi nguyn liu chanh v mui. Chng s gip mn ph kin thi trang ca bn sng bng nh mi.  thc hin bn cn:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000230642/file/ve-sinh-tui-da-6_c4abdd28a7d44862b312314f4d545d06.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Chanh v mui gip lm sch ti da nhanh v tit kim</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 1:</strong>&nbsp;Ly na qu chanh sau  chm vo mt cht mui ri tin hnh ch tht nh ln nhng vt bn bm</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 2:</strong>&nbsp;Sau khi thc hin bn  trong vng t 3 n 5 pht th dng khn mm thm cht nc m ri lau li b mt ti va lm sch</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 3:</strong>&nbsp;t ti  ni kh thong  kh t nhin l c th s dng</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"dung_aceton_de_ve_sinh_tui_da\">Dng Aceton  v sinh ti da</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Aceton l dung dch ty sn mng tay c s dng kh ph bin. Bn cnh lm sch hiu qu b mt da, cht ny cn c kh nng loi b i cc vt bn kh x l nh mu bm trn ti da. Hy bt u tin hnh:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000230642/file/ve-sinh-tui-da-5_c0d78b1879d44d3589219e1deb32e54b.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Aceton s gip bn nh bay bi bn cng u trn ti da trng</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 1:&nbsp;</strong>Lm sch mi bi bn trn b mt ti da bng khn kh</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 2:</strong>&nbsp;Dng vi mm hoc bng ty trang, sau  thm cht aceton ri lau nh vo nhng v tr vt bn</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 3:</strong>&nbsp;Bn i 15 giy ri dng vi mm thm nc m lau li ti</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 4</strong>: Dng 1 t vaseline bi ln v mt ti  da khng b kh hay phai mu</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Lu : Khi dng aceton bn khng nn lm dng qu nhiu v khng nn  dung dch bm ln da qu lu. iu ny c th khin cho da b phai mu</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"meo_cham_soc_va_bao_quan_tui_da_trang_luon_dep_nhu_moi\">Mo chm sc v bo qun ti da trng lun p nh mi</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"cach_cham_soc_tui_da\">Cch chm sc ti da</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000230642/file/1_6069878c16b744bcbb6603e24e796f17.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Chm sc ti da thng xuyn hn  sn phm lun nh mi</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Phng nga l bc u tin bn c th thc hin trong hnh trnh chm sc ti da. Sau khi s dng sau mt ngy, hy lau sch vi khn bng mm  loi b bi bn dnh vo. Nu c th hy dng xt bo v  da  to thm lp bo v  da, gip y li vt bn v hi m mc.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Khi ti xut hin bt k tnh trng mc hay bn bm cn c x l nhanh chng, trnh tnh trng  lu ngy c th khin vt bn xm nhp su vo bn trong, lm cho ti da kh v sinh hn hoc thm ch l gim i cht lng ca lp da</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Khng bao gi  nc ngm vo ti da trng ca bn. Nu ti da b t, hy ly khn bng trng sch thm kh, sau   kh t nhin  nhit  phng, khng sy nng hoc phi kh ngoi nng, bi iu ny s lm da b kh nt</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Bn nn b xung cht dng cho ti da thng xuyn hn, s dng ph 1 lp ln b mt ti da s gip sn phm va bng p va tng  n hi, gip ti s dng lu bn hn</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"cach_bao_quan_tui_da\">Cch bo qun ti da</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> chic ti xch ca bn c th s dng c lu v gi c mu sc cng nh cht lng ca n, ngoi vic chm sc ti thng xuyn bn cng nn bit cch bo qun sn phm ng n  gip gi c trng thi tt nht, lc no cng trng nh mi</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000230642/file/ve-sinh-tui-da-7_ff94ed7720ab4921ae09dd0270bfcfab.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Bo qun ti da s s dng lu bn hn</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li> gip xch  ni thong mt, trnh   nhng khu vc tip xc trc tip vi nh sng mt tri hoc nhng ni m mc, c nhit  thp</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Nu bn khng c nhu cu s dng ti xch trong thi gian di lu th nn nhi mt lp bng hoc giy vo bn trong ti. iu ny s gip cho ti xch c th gi c form dng nh ban u</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li> ti  ni kh ro, thong mt khi khng s dng, khi ct gi nn cho sn phm vo hp hoc bc ti bng  ngoi  trnh bi bn bm dnh ln ti da.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Bn c th s dng mt t bt baking soda  kh mi cho chic ti xch da ca mnh. Hy cho mt t baking soda vo ti, sau  bc trong v gi hoc ti dustbag trong 24 gi, chic ti ca bn s thm tho nh lc mi mua</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khng qu phc tp  lm sch ti da b bm bn, ch cn bn tinh  v p dng nhng cch v sinh ti da mu trng c chia s trn bn c th gi c v p tinh khi nh lc mi mua cho chic ti da ca mnh ri.  s hu c ph kin ti da cht lng, mu m mi nht th trng, n ngay viBitis.com.vnbn nh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Tit l cch v sinh ti da mu trng nhanh chng, hiu qu', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '348-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-10-11 14:46:21', '2023-10-11 14:46:21', '', 348, 'https://minhhoang04.demopolyct.online/?p=351', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(353, 1, '2023-10-11 14:48:36', '2023-10-11 14:48:36', '<!-- wp:html /-->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"uu_diem_cua_viec_lam_sach_giay_trang_ma_khong_can_giat\">u im ca vic lm sch giy trng m khng cn git</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>C rt nhiu phng php v sinh giy trng hiu qu, tuy nhin vic p dng cng thc lm sch giy trng khng cn git c rt nhiu ngi la chn, bi:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000230642/file/lam-sach-giay-trang-1_31203de2bb4e400d934a901b1563038a.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Nhiu u im ca vic lm sch giy trng m khng cn phi git</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Lm sch nhanh: Vic bn git giy bng nc s phi mt t 30 n 60 pht v mt thm t 1 n 2 ngy  giy kh hn. Ring vi cch lm sch ny, i giy yu thch ca bn ch cn t 10 n 20 pht l  c th tip tc s dng</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Gia tng tui th cho giy: Cch git giy thng thng s lm nh hng n phn keo dn ca giy. Ring vi phng php v sinh giy khng cn git s lm gia tng mc s dng giy lu di hn</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Gi c dng giy: Vi bt k cch git giy trng no nu bn git qu nhiu giy s nhanh phai mu, mt i form dng. Nhng ring vi cch lm sch khng cn git s hn ch ti a tnh trng giy b mt form</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Tit kim chi ph: Lm sch giy m khng cn git bng nhng nguyn liu c sn trong nh, iu ny va tin li, n gin m cn t tn chi ph v cng sc cho bn</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"cach_lam_sach_giay_trang_khong_can_giat_hieu_qua\">Cch lm sch giy trng khng cn git hiu qu</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>V sinh giy trng khng qu kh khn, nhng nu khng bit cch v sinh ng n, cc vt bn c th s kh c lm sch tht s. Di y l mt s gii php v sinh giy khng cn phi git, loi b c cc vt , bn bm trn giy trng m vn gi c  bn cho sn phm.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"su_dung_kem_danh_rang\">S dng kem nh rng</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kem nh rng khng ch s dng  v sinh rng ming mi ngy m n cn l loi hp cht c kh nng lm sch, ty vt bn, vt mc, vt  vng trn giy trng hiu qu.  thc hin bn p dng cc bc nh sau:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000230642/file/lam-sach-giay-trang-2_f65f2fa7408c4d3dbebcc04198880117.png\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Kem nh rng c cng dng ty trng giy hiu qu</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 1:</strong>&nbsp;Bn dng ming vi bng, sau  thm mt cht nc m ln vi ri nh nhng lau u b mt giy. Bn ch cn b mt giy hi m thi ch khng nn  thm t qu nhiu</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 2:</strong>&nbsp;Tip theo bn cho mt t kem nh rng ln nhng vt bn cn v sinh, sau  dng bn chi chi nh nhng theo chuyn ng trn  lm sch vt bn</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 3:</strong>&nbsp;i 10 pht</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 4:</strong>&nbsp;Dng mt ming khn t lau sch phn kem nh rng trn giy. Bn c th lau li 2 ln  chc chn lm sch lng kem nh rng trn giy</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 5:</strong>&nbsp;t giy ca bn di nh nng mt tri hay trc qut  giy kh hon ton. i giy ca bn s p nh mi</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"su_dung_chanh_tuoi\">S dng chanh ti</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Axit trong chanh ti c tc dng rt tt trong vic lm sch giy trng. Nhng vt bn t bn bm trn giy s bin mt nhanh chng nh vic v sinh bng chanh ti.  thc hin bn tin hnh theo cc bc sau:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000230642/file/chanh-tuoi_1405ea354ced43f994f2e44888fbe186.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Chanh ti mang li hiu qu lm sch k diu, t tn chi ph</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 1:&nbsp;</strong>Bn ct i qu chanh v vt ly nc ct, sau  trn vi 3 phn nc</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 2:</strong>&nbsp;Dng hn hp bi ln cc vt bn  loi b chng i. Lu  hy ch xt mnh ln nhng vt  vng</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 3:</strong>&nbsp;Dng khn thm nc sch v lau ln ch va lm sch  loi b i bi bn v chanh tha</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 4:</strong>&nbsp;em giy phi  ngoi nng hoc dng my sy kh l c th s dng giy</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"ve_sinh_giay_trang_bang_thuoc_tay\">V sinh giy trng bng thuc ty</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thuc ty c u im l lm sch vt bn mt cch nhanh chng, tiu dit vi khun v kh mi hi kh chu rt hiu qu. Nn bn c th p dng trn i giy trng ang bm bn ca mnh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000230642/file/giay-trang_bbb0b546111a4203ae431232037d10fe.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Thuc ty s gip loi b vt bn v kh mi giy trng</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 1:</strong>&nbsp;Pha long thuc ty vi nc theo t l 1:5 (1 phn thuc ty: 5 phn nc)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 2</strong>: Dng bn chi nhng vo nc ty pha long, sau  ch trc tip ln cc vt 