->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nu bn ang cn s dng giy trng ngay lp tc th nn dng ru trng hoc hn hp cn  lm sch i giy ca mnh. C hai cht ny u c tnh bay hi nn s kh rt nhanh. Cch thc hin v cng n gin</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000230642/file/lam-sach-giay-trang-3_192981cde3ef4bd1b9e16d603e9efde2.png\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Cn v ru trng c hiu qu lm sch giy tc th</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 1:</strong>&nbsp;Bn dng vi  thm cn hoc ru ri ch nh ln giy nht l nhng ni c vt bn.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 2:</strong>&nbsp;Tip tc lau cho n khi vt bn c loi b hon ton</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Bc 3:</strong>&nbsp;Phi kh giy di nng nh hoc ni c gi</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"luu_y_bao_quan_giay_trang_lau_nhat_cho_ban\">Lu  bo qun giy trng lu nht cho bn</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So vi nhng loi giy khc th giy trng l loi giy nhanh c nht nu khng bit cch bo qun. V vy nhng lu  sau y s hu ch cho bn trong vic gi giy trng nh mi, lu d, khng b  vng</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000230642/file/lam-sach-giay-trang_b11f5463e72e4367883ad8c28201b892.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Lu   bo qun giy trng lun sch p nh mi</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Git giy: Bn nn xem xt cht liu  tm ra cch git ph hp nht. Git giy ng cch s gip cho giy khng b sn vi, loi b c hon ton vt bn</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Phi giy: Phi giy l cng on quyt nh rt nhiu n  mi ca i giy. Tuy n gin nht nhng cn phi phi ng cch. Hy chn nhng v tr  trn cao, kh thong v c gi nh</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>V tr ct gi: Do giy trng rt d b bm bi bn nn hy bo qun chng vo ti nilon hoc hp giy trc khi  giy ln k hoc cho vo t giy. ng thi, bn cng phi lu  v tr t k giy, t giy kh thong, trnh nh nng mt tri</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Thng xuyn v sinh, lau chi: Hy v sinh, lm sch cc vt bn khi cn mi, lc ny vic v sinh s nhanh chng v d hn. ng  nhng i giy b bm bn lu ngy ri mi mang i git, lc ny nhng vt bn s cng u v kh c th nh bay hon ton.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vi cc mo v cch lm sch giy trng khng cn git n gin bn trn, bn hon ton c th t lm mi cho i giy ca mnh ngay ti nh vi chi ph cc thp. Va tin li va an ton khng lm nh hng n cht lng ca i giy. Thng xuyn theo di blogs&nbsp;Bitis.com.vn&nbsp; c cp nht nhiu tin tc hu ch nh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Mch bn cch lm sch giy trng khng cn git hiu qu ngay ti nh', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '353-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-10-11 14:54:58', '2023-10-11 14:54:58', '', 353, 'https://minhhoang04.demopolyct.online/?p=357', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
